track.name: Life for Rent
comments: ♥♥great song, great CD, great voice...♥♥
If I was a groupie, I had to say "marry me". So all I can say is great lyrics :)
I first heard this song when I was 12, now I'm 22 and it still has my most favourite lyrics of all time <3 Miss Dido writing masterpieces like this.

Anything she sings sounds great!!! (2) Where have I been all my life? Not being funny...I only found Dido when I stumbled onto last.fm. That speaks volumes about how pathetic radio in the U.S. has become...with corporate playlists. Dido is right at the top of a select few I would gladly hear anytime and would travel far to see. If you haven't seen the acoustic videos from her new album, treat youself...they are right here. My favorites are Dido - Girl Who Got Away (Acoustic) and Dido - No Freedom (Acoustic). The CD I ordered should be in my mitts by Friday. Can't wait.
The lyrics are meaningful, and this song is pretty beautiful! [2] i love her voice...i love her music....she is great!!!
I have often thought that I would love to live by the sea, to travel the world alone and live more simply, I have no idea what's happened to that dream . . .
One of my most favorite songs of all time <3. Add me if we have Super musical compatibility ^^!
It's just a thought. Only a thought... [2]
Duuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuull.
still being supreme
Amazing song... It reaches my heart so easily.
Amazing voice !!!!
'Cos nothing I have is truly mine
This song is so beautiful...
So nice...
This song is so beautiful. I love it. Dido is so freaking awesome.
Oh wow.  This song is amazing.  Lyrics and all, I couldn't have said it better myself.  Theme song for the year.  <3 <3 <3
Dido is my Love!!!
Simplesmente adoro a Dido! Meu CD "No Angel" está quase furado!
